@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Create an account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry/Unregistered user
CreateAccount : do/Create account
CreateAccount : exit/Account created

state "Watch videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry/Registered user
WatchVideos : do/Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit/Videos watched

state "Upload video" as UploadVideo
UploadVideo : entry/Registered user
UploadVideo : do/Upload video
UploadVideo : exit/Video uploaded

state "Save video in likes list" as SaveInLikesList
SaveInLikesList : entry/User watching videos
SaveInLikesList : do/Save video to likes list
SaveInLikesList : exit/Video saved

state "View saved videos" as ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos : entry/User with saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : do/View saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : exit/Videos viewed

state "Enter discussion option" as EnterDiscussionOption
EnterDiscussionOption : entry/User watching videos
EnterDiscussionOption : do/Enter discussion option
EnterDiscussionOption : exit/Discussion entered

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos

WatchVideos --> SaveInLikesList
SaveInLikesList --> ViewSavedVideos

ViewSavedVideos --> EnterDiscussionOption
EnterDiscussionOption --> [*]

@enduml
